[6.348, "o", "\u001b[2mUsed: scene_init, scene_add, scene_lint\u001b[22m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "✅ **Demo project created** at `./demo` (16:9, 5s root duration).\r\n\r\n✅ **Added scene**: \"hello\" (announcement preset, narration: \"Hello vibe agent\", 5s duration). No audio/image generated. Spliced into `index.html` at 0-5s.\r\n\r\n✅ **Lint**: Clean (0 errors/warnings). 2 info notes on GSAP CDN script (standard, no action needed for preview/render).\r\n\r\nNext: `scene_render` to export MP4, or edit scenes with `scene_add`.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m(2 turns)\u001b[22m\r\n"]
[0.007, "o", "\u001b[1;33m→ scene_init → scene_add → scene_lint, planned and executed by Grok in 2 turns.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
